[normal]Q226 [bold]&#xa0; 
[normal]Ian Mearns:[bold] This is the section that I should have been asking questions about now.  We talked before about perverse incentives within the system.  Given the growing diversity of our school estate and the growing independence of secondary schools, is there not a danger that, having 14
